item.title: CVE-2019-0266|2024-08-04T17:44:16.422Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20hana%20extended%20application%20services%2C%20advanced%20model%20%28xs%20advanced%29
item.description: Under certain conditions SAP HANA Extended Application Services, version 1.0, advanced model (XS advanced) writes credentials of platform users to a trace file of the SAP HANA system. Even though this trace file is protected from unauthorized access, the risk of leaking information is increased.
